    "description": "Jae 成为了梦寐以求的制作人，即将执导 1999 年最热门的真人秀《心动小屋》！这档节目的要求很高，不过风险更高。每一季她都必须亲自选角、拍摄并制作。你将化身 Jae，投身全球顶尖奢华的马里布豪宅，捕捉恋情萌芽的浪漫瞬间和爆点十足的戏剧性场面，打造每一季都独一无二的热辣节目。然后千万别忘了满足狂热观众的要求，否则节目可能被迫停播。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/3e6af39632fb244c5bfdb5d96698edb7.poster.avif?t=1746465607\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/3e6af39632fb244c5bfdb5d96698edb7.webm?t=1746465607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/3e6af39632fb244c5bfdb5d96698edb7.mp4?t=1746465607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每一季节目你都将选择不同的嘉宾，满足观众善变刁钻的要求，造就了这档节目贯穿始终的独特风格。节目开播越久，问题便会逐渐浮现。嘉宾们为什么对“Crush 饮料”如此依赖？“胜利滑滑乐”又到哪里去了？你可以试试私下交谈，或是老派一点暗中偷窥，有助于揭发真相……前提是“高层”不来搅局。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/4af02c002d919b787b0d2beece2b7742.poster.avif?t=1746465607\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/4af02c002d919b787b0d2beece2b7742.webm?t=1746465607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/4af02c002d919b787b0d2beece2b7742.mp4?t=1746465607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >节目选角季季新</h2>你将从 12 名性格古怪的参加者中，挑选 4 名嘉宾参加每季节目。混搭性格对立或互补的迷人组合，欣赏针锋相对和火花四射的场面。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/8524b93254fc15cca3701236c98ef5f9.poster.avif?t=1746465607\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/8524b93254fc15cca3701236c98ef5f9.webm?t=1746465607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/8524b93254fc15cca3701236c98ef5f9.mp4?t=1746465607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >观众口味要遵循</h2>只要是家里有电视的人都会看《心动小屋》！包括美食家、单亲老爸、屁屁专家和……灯塔学家……？为了娱乐各个圈子的特定观众，你必须精心策划才能收服所有人的心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/f8f20f193ce34fb0c84cab2c4909f277.poster.avif?t=1746465607\" width=615 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/f8f20f193ce34fb0c84cab2c4909f277.webm?t=1746465607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >播送广告赚大钱</h2>如此优良的娱乐节目可是很烧钱的。放下相机，偶尔播放一些有品味的电视广告来赚进钞票吧。每天晚上你都能用这笔可观的广告收入为豪宅添购新家具，以此为观众和嘉宾带来新气象。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/78c564d9ccd71eb58a74770275aca0f9.poster.avif?t=1746465607\" width=615 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337820/extras/78c564d9ccd71eb58a74770275aca0f9.webm?t=1746465607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拨云见雾揭秘辛</h2>夜晚下播后，你可以大胆探索豪宅。打破规矩，和嘉宾来场禁忌谈话，揭露《心动小屋》不可告人的秘密！",
